"},{"pid":"bd39f4b274addeba22bc5e1aa89aaa09245c1925","tid":1384844,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:12:51.000Z","msg":"繼續努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8911921bb8eb4a28add258dde3363fdfeefa7b4d","tid":1384844,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:13:06.000Z","msg":"Hong Kongers are similarly displeased at the sense that they are no longer masters of their own fates and are gradually being absorbed and assimilated into the rest of China, from which they still consider themselves to have a unique identity."},{"pid":"e0e653cd49cdf77c3ea7e485ceb05ccefb1d8ad0","tid":1384844,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:13:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推! 8月5罷工!!!!! </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日(7月30)1500-2000</span></span>會有義工係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">旺角東天橋</span></span>擺街站等無上連登的市民都可以寫底感受比我地,希望大家支持<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">餓住的小朋友入一入黎, 有心幫佢地都可以黎睇下</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1382980/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1382980/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a><br />\nTG:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkrevolutiondocument\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkrevolutiondocument&d=HYT0XJgSPTYEb9NwUTCrmh0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=386521eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkrevolutiondocument</a><br />\nFB:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%